\section{Results and Analysis}
\label{sec:results}
% ============================================================

This section presents experimental results from BookSim2 cycle-accurate simulations on Mesh $4\times4$ (16 nodes). We compare GNNocRoute-PPO against six baseline routing algorithms across three traffic patterns and six injection rates. Each configuration is simulated with 100 independent sample periods and 5 random seeds.

