Key observations from Table~\ref{tab:latency}:
\begin{itemize}
    \item Under \textbf{uniform traffic}, all minimal routing algorithms perform similarly (19.6--22.0 cycles). GNNocRoute-PPO achieves 19.8 cycles, comparable to XY (19.6). Planar Adaptive and ROMM (22.0 and 20.3) remain competitive. Valiant is significantly worse (39.7) due to its non-minimal path selection.
